322. Coin Change
You are given an integer array coins representing coins of different denominations and an integer amount representing a total amount of money.
Return the fewest number of coins that you need to make up that amount. If that amount of money cannot be made up by any combination of the coins, return -1.
You may assume that you have an infinite number of each kind of coin.

Example 1:
Input: coins = [1,2,5], amount = 11
Output: 3
Explanation: 11 = 5 + 5 + 1

Example 2:
Input: coins = [2], amount = 3
Output: -1

Example 3:
Input: coins = [1], amount = 0
Output: 0

Approach 1-top down approach
class Solution {
    public int coinChange(int[] coins, int amount) {
        int[] dp=new int[amount+1];
        Arrays.fill(dp,Integer.MAX_VALUE);
        return coinChangeHelper(coins,amount,dp);
    }
    public int coinChangeHelper(int[] coins,int remAmount,int[] dp){
         int n=coins.length;
        if(remAmount==0){
            return 0;
        }
        if(remAmount<0){
            return -1;
        }
        if(dp[remAmount] != Integer.MAX_VALUE){
            return dp[remAmount];
        }
        int minCoin=Integer.MAX_VALUE; 
        for(int i=0;i<n;i++){
           int res=coinChangeHelper (coins,remAmount -coins[i],dp);
           if(res!=-1){
                minCoin=Math.min(minCoin,1+res);
           }
        }
        dp[remAmount]=(minCoin==Integer.MAX_VALUE)?-1:minCoin;
        return dp[remAmount];

    }
}

Final Answer
Time Complexity: O(amount × n)
Space Complexity: O(amount)

Approach-2 (Bottom up Approach)
class Solution {
    public int coinChange(int[] coins, int amount) {
        int n=amount;
        int[] dp=new int[n+1];
        Arrays.fill(dp,Integer.MAX_VALUE/2);
        dp[0]=0;
        for(int rem=1;rem<=n;rem++){
           for(int j=0;j<coins.length;j++){
            int remAmount=rem-coins[j];
            if(remAmount>=0){
                dp[rem]=Math.min(dp[rem],1+dp[remAmount]);
            }
           }
        }
        return dp[n]==Integer.MAX_VALUE/2? -1 :dp[n];
    }
}
time: O(amount × coins)
space: O(amount)


